data.description: Great! Great! News all agents and the Buyer This house was Appraisal at the price of $519,000 But we are listed at $509,990 Because seller need quick closing and we have a report in hand  please ask for it if you need . Welcome home to one of Aurora most desirable neighborhoods in Auburn Hill .Nice and beautiful House .BEAUTIFUL CURB APPEAL! NICELY MAINTAINED WITH SUNNY OPEN FLOOR PLAN. SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM, KITCHEN WITH TILE FLOORING + ALL APPLIANCE STAY, ADJOINING DINING AREA WITH DESIGNER LIGHTING. LARGE MASTER FEATURES WALK-IN CLOSET & PRIVATE BATH, CONVENIENT MAIN FLOOR LAUNDRY & GUEST BATH. PRIVATE BACKYARD HAS OVERSIZED PATIO & STORAGE SHED. 2 CAR OVERSIZED GARAGE + EXTRA LARGE DRIVEWAY .. YOU WILL LOVE THIS ONE! Come and see this beautiful house which has three bedrooms with two full bathrooms upstairs and the other one-half bath on the main floor. The open kitchen space and great living room  . All the interior house has new paint with brand new Dishwasher , all windows blinds covering are new, and the two new windows was installed  in the master bedroom. Kitchen countertop and cabinet are new paint with professional housekeeping. The carpet is deep cleaned by professional person . Please wear the shoes "BOOTIES" Set the showing online at the showing Time ( 303-573-7469).or broker bay (1888-808-0331).Buyer's agent is responsible to verify square footage and HOA information. Provide the Pre- Qualification lender letter or POF with your offer. Overlapping is allowed for this listing. Seller has the right to accept best offer at any time. The seller will need a 24-hour response time.Showing is to go and show,
